Class LinkedQueue

  • java.lang.Object

    Queue
    public class LinkedQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue
    This is a linked implementation of the interface Queue. This linked implementation is called LinkedQueue. In this implementation, we are using the head-and-tail approach.
